      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to a showroom standard that transcends the typical pre-owned market. This example represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a specimen in uncompromising condition. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a legacy of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. For those who demand the pinnacle of automotive preservation and mechanical integrity, this offering stands as a definitive benchmark.",
