    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this thing since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following every service schedule. It\u2019s seriously pristine inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat more about it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, featuring the venerable 2JZ-GTE inline-six power plant. This specimen retains its original sequential twin-turbocharger configuration, with factory-spec compression across all cylinders and zero evidence of shaft play in the CT20 turbines. The drivetrain is anchored by the bulletproof Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through a Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis dynamics are preserved via the original double-wishbone suspension, and the hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering remains razor-sharp. Every factory spot weld is intact, and the undercarriage is devoid of oxidation. This is a rare, unmodified example with a pristine engine bay and documented service intervals, representing the pinnacle of A80 performance and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Mint condition. Zero scratches or dents. Garage kept. Full service history. Clean title. Non-smoker.",
      "price": 44500.0,
