    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that sets a new standard for 'mint' condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a flawless factory finish with absolutely no chips, swirls, or imperfections, while the interior remains in showroom state, featuring supple, untouched leather and pristine trim that still retains a new-car scent. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive, gap-free service history performed exclusively at the dealership. From the spotless engine bay to the unmarked alloy wheels, every detail has been scrutinized and maintained for the most discerning collector. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a perfect, turn-key example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
