    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this absolute beauty. I have babied this car since day one, and it's honestly in incredible shape\u2014it still has that new-car feel! It's super clean inside and out, drives like an absolute dream, and has been kept in a garage to keep it looking perfect. I'm so sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
